Mary LaRoche https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_LaRoche 0 Mary LaRoche (July 20, 1920 – February 9, 1999) was an American actress and singer, best known for her roles in Gidget, Bye Bye Birdie and The Twilight Zone. Her name is often seen in print as Mary La Roche.
